578
00:40:29.090 --> 00:40:30.090
Go!

579
00:40:37.930 --> 00:40:39.500
This is bad.

580
00:40:42.080 --> 00:40:43.340
Are you sick?

581
00:40:47.870 --> 00:40:48.870
Captain.

582
00:40:48.900 --> 00:40:51.380
That asshole moved to
Do-hyun's room.

583
00:40:55.690 --> 00:40:58.120
Actually. he has a friend
in maintenance.

584
00:40:58.360 --> 00:40:59.829
Yeah. the mop head.

585
00:40:59.830 --> 00:41:00.830
Yeah. him.

586
00:41:02.490 --> 00:41:04.870
