619
00:43:26.680 --> 00:43:27.680
31.

620
00:43:28.300 --> 00:43:28.960
One.

621
00:43:28.960 --> 00:43:29.960
One. two.

622
00:43:30.490 --> 00:43:31.580
Gosh…

623
00:43:32.900 --> 00:43:33.900
From the beginning.

624
00:43:35.070 --> 00:43:36.369
