625
00:43:36.370 --> 00:43:38.129
Focus on your chest!

626
00:43:38.130 --> 00:43:39.350
Hey! Together.

627
00:43:39.700 --> 00:43:40.980
Together. together. together.

628
00:43:43.290 --> 00:43:44.580
Eating is training. too.

629
00:43:44.970 --> 00:43:47.610
You have to be
bigger and heavier.

630
00:43:48.690 --> 00:43:49.690
Enjoy.

631
00:43:57.500 --> 00:43:59.550
Don't kick
with the top of your foot.

632
00:43:59.690 --> 00:44:00.690
Seven.

633
00:44:01.410 --> 00:44:03.490
Do it slowly or you'll get hurt.

634
00:44:06.650 --> 00:44:07.650
Seven.

635
00:44:08.070 --> 00:44:08.760
Eight!

636
00:44:08.910 --> 00:44:09.960
Pull all the way.

637
00:44:10.880 --> 00:44:11.880
Open up your chest.

638
00:44:15.360 --> 00:44:16.360
Don't stop the kick.

639
00:44:24.100 --> 00:44:25.559
Squeeze it out!

640
00:44:25.560 --> 00:44:26.560
Run!

641
00:44:30.300 --> 00:44:31.770
Okay! More!

642
00:44:37.090 --> 00:44:38.339
Tuck your chin.

643
00:44:38.340 --> 00:44:39.340
Your chin!

644
