800
00:54:04.880 --> 00:54:05.700
What?

801
00:54:05.840 --> 00:54:07.360
This crazy-ass prick.

802
00:54:07.680 --> 00:54:08.410
You little...

803
00:54:08.680 --> 00:54:09.920
Don't cuss.

804
00:54:10.000 --> 00:54:11.379
Don't cuss you son of a bitch.

805
00:54:11.380 --> 00:54:12.380
You damn…

806
00:54:13.220 --> 00:54:14.220
You okay?

807
00:54:14.440 --> 00:54:15.100
Hey.

808
00:54:15.190 --> 00:54:16.509
You did bring him!

809
00:54:16.510 --> 00:54:17.609
You should've told us.

810
00:54:17.610 --> 00:54:18.779
Good job.

811
00:54:18.780 --> 00:54:20.409
You idiot!
Why did you come?

812
00:54:20.410 --> 00:54:22.620
To get his ass beat
you shithole.

813
00:54:23.450 --> 00:54:24.550
I'm taking Hyun-min.

814
00:54:26.490 --> 00:54:27.490
Eyes down.

815
00:54:28.140 --> 00:54:29.400
Eyes down!

816
00:54:30.690 --> 00:54:32.200
I said eyes down
you piece of shit!

817
00:54:42.130 --> 00:54:43.130
Let's go.

818
00:54:43.440 --> 00:54:43.850
Shit...

819
00:54:44.250 --> 00:54:45.250
Hold on.

820
00:54:45.560 --> 00:54:46.560
Hey.

821
00:54:46.950 --> 00:54:48.000
Crazy asshole!

822
00:55:10.100 --> 00:55:11.100
You!

823
00:55:11.310 --> 00:55:12.590
Bring him no matter what.

824
00:55:13.100 --> 00:55:14.509
If you don't. you'll die.

825
00:55:14.510 --> 00:55:15.510
Yes. sir.

826
00:55:16.320 --> 00:55:17.400
Dipshits...

827
00:55:17.890 --> 00:55:18.890
