828
00:55:30.520 --> 00:55:31.520
Excuse me.

829
00:55:33.700 --> 00:55:34.700
Damn.

830
00:55:35.330 --> 00:55:36.330
Excuse me!

831
00:55:38.470 --> 00:55:39.599
It's just that...

832
00:55:39.600 --> 00:55:41.690
