quick chat with him.

833
00:55:43.940 --> 00:55:45.850
What do you have to talk about?

834
00:55:46.120 --> 00:55:47.120
Oh...!

835
00:55:48.730 --> 00:55:49.730
Hey!

836
00:55:50.200 --> 00:55:51.480
You tell him.

837
00:55:59.610 --> 00:56:00.770
