838
00:56:06.570 --> 00:56:07.570
Go on.

839
00:56:09.510 --> 00:56:11.190
We won't be long.
Thank you.

840
00:56:11.520 --> 00:56:12.520
Thank you.

841
00:56:29.000 --> 00:56:30.110
The prick's here.

842
00:56:40.340 --> 00:56:41.340
Get up!

843
00:56:51.560 --> 00:56:54.020
